to follow in his footsteps.

1276
01:01:54,428 --> 01:01:55,560
Mm-hmm.

1277
01:01:55,596 --> 01:02:00,065
But, you know,
it just wasn't me.

1278
01:02:00,100 --> 01:02:02,501
You know, I had,
I had to find my own path.

1279
