I like that.

1292
01:02:37,204 --> 01:02:38,503
I guess.

1293
01:02:38,539 --> 01:02:42,507
I think after my dad was gone,

1294
01:02:42,543 --> 01:02:45,177
the only thing
she was holding on to was

1295
