me following his legacy.

1296
01:02:46,780 --> 01:02:48,513
Wow.

1297
01:02:48,549 --> 01:02:51,016
So, yeah, on-on the surface,

1298
01:02:51,051 --> 01:02:54,686
she loves to talk
about her son, the artist.

1299
01:02:54,721 --> 01:02:59,424
But I know she would prefer
her son, the doctor.

1300
