As a single mother
who had to raise her child...

1309
01:03:28,155 --> 01:03:30,222
it's hard.

1310
01:03:30,257 --> 01:03:31,790
And I mean, we just trying.

1311
01:03:31,825 --> 01:03:34,292
You know, that's all we doing.
We just trying.

1312
01:03:34,328 --> 01:03:37,729
It's all trial and error,
and error and trial and...

1313
01:03:37,764 --> 01:03:40,832
[inhales]
You know, if we could just

1314
01:03:40,867 --> 01:03:43,735
help our children not to suffer
any heartache,

1315
01:03:43,770 --> 01:03:46,605
if we could spare them that,
and just give 'em the option

1316
01:03:46,640 --> 01:03:49,307
that they can go down
another road in a different path

1317
01:03:49,343 --> 01:03:52,811
that's just a little higher
than what we had to go down...

1318
01:03:55,182 --> 01:03:58,483
-You know what, Ms. Hamilton?
-What?

1319
01:04:00,520 --> 01:04:02,854
You're not that bad.

1320
01:04:02,889 --> 01:04:06,157
-That's all you got?
-You're pretty good.

1321
01:04:06,193 --> 01:04:07,659
-Okay. Thank you.
-You're pretty good.

1322
01:04:07,694 --> 01:04:09,594
And you know what?
You go on call me Ms. H.

1323
01:04:09,630 --> 01:04:12,163
Ms. H? I can call you Ms. H now?

1324
01:04:12,199 --> 01:04:13,698
-Holler.
-Okay.

1325
01:04:13,734 --> 01:04:15,717
-Okay.
-No, these ain't bad.

