01:08:00,544 --> 01:08:03,444
I'm sorry, Brittney.

1398
01:08:03,480 --> 01:08:05,680
-I'm sorry.
-No.

1399
01:08:05,715 --> 01:08:08,850
You got what you wanted, right?

1400
01:08:08,885 --> 01:08:11,519
And I've always respected that
about you.

1401
01:08:11,555 --> 01:08:15,990
Your by-any-means-necessary
approach to get what you want.

1402
01:08:16,026 --> 01:08:18,059
I just didn't know
that it applied to me.

1403
01:08:19,629 --> 01:08:22,096
-Baby.
-I'm not your baby.

1404
01:08:25,168 --> 01:08:28,970
Wow. I'm sorry.

1405
01:08:36,079 --> 01:08:38,112
You're not gonna go
after your mother?

1406
01:08:39,749 --> 01:08:41,449
I'm trying to be here for you
right now.

1407
01:08:41,484 --> 01:08:44,152
Right now was when
I was calling you earlier.

1408
01:08:44,187 --> 01:08:47,355
God, it's like
you are so freaking impulsive.

1409
01:08:47,390 --> 01:08:49,524
You know,
it seems romantic and exciting,

1410
01:08:49,559 --> 01:08:51,092
but really, it's inconsiderate.

1411
01:08:53,029 --> 01:08:55,496
You'd have some accountability,
Amiri.

1412
01:08:57,701 --> 01:09:00,869
I love that you're spontaneous,

1413
01:09:00,904 --> 01:09:02,770
that you're not married
to time...

1414
01:09:04,074 --> 01:09:08,176
but there really has to be
something

1415
