-Mm.

1429
01:10:51,097 --> 01:10:52,697
I know sharing that had to hurt.

1430
01:10:52,732 --> 01:10:56,100
Ugh. More than you know.

1431
01:10:56,136 --> 01:10:59,570
Well, it's only fair
that I return the favor.

1432
01:10:59,606 --> 01:11:03,041
Uh, you don't have to.

